Unfortunately, it was not possible to promote the expansion of <0xC4><0x8C>T<0xC3><0x9A>'s rights in the field of economic competition in telecommunications until the recently approved telecommunications law was updated, despite the fact that, from this, many experts expected the situation to improve.
